title: #92Noon! Parody/Gleeman/Durham/Grimm/Birk/Zimm
description: We open with Pastor Jeremy and a fresh parody from Nordo, Gleeman in studio, vox-to-vox with Falcons voice Wes Durham, Mike Grimm on Gophers hoops, the weekly Birk Bit for a half hour, then Zimmer's presser/wrap!
